---
import "../styles/global.css";

import Page from "../layouts/index.astro";
---

<Page
  page_title="Cake & Frosting Flavors - Sweet Bakes Chicago Menu Guide."
  page_description="See our complete list of popular cake, filling, and frosting flavors to help you design your perfect custom cake or cupcake order."
>

<section class="w-full">
  <div class="w-full h-44 md:h-64 bg-gray-100">
    <img src="/cake-hero-cupcakes.avif" alt="Cakes hero" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
  </div>
</section>

<main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 space-y-12">
  <section class="prose lg:prose-lg">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Cakes & Flavors</h1>
    <p>We offer a wide range of classic and specialty cake flavors. All cakes are made in our nut-free
      facility. If you have dietary needs (gluten-free, dairy-free, sugar-free) please contact us
      to confirm availability for specific designs.</p>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Base style for custom bullets */
    .list-with-svgs {
      list-style: none;
      /* Remove default bullet */
      padding-left: 0;
      /* Adjust padding if needed */
    }

    .list-with-svgs li {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 28px;
      /* Space for the SVG */
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      /* Adjust spacing between list items */
    }

    .list-with-svgs li::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 20px;
      /* SVG width */
      height: 20px;
      /* SVG height */
      background-size: contain;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center;
    }

    /* Specific SVG styles */
    .list-with-svgs .white-cake::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/cake-thin-white-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .yellow-cake::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/cake-thin-yellow-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    /* Assuming you want a default chocolate SVG, if not, adjust */
    .list-with-svgs .chocolate-cake::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/cake-thin-chocolate-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .red-velvet-cake::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/cake-thin-red-velvet-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .strawberry-cake::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/strawberry-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .lemon-cake::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/lemon-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .lime-cake::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/lime-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .raspberry-cake::before {
      /* You don't have a raspberry SVG in your list, using berry for now */
      background-image: url('/svgs/berry-cooking-food-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .marble-cake::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/marble-cake-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .mocha-flavor::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/mocha-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .coffee-flavor::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/coffee-bean-filled-roast-brew-svgrepo-com.svg');
    }

    .list-with-svgs .cinnamon-flavor::before {
      background-image: url('/svgs/cinnamon.svg');
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Traditional Flavors -->
  <section class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
  
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Cake Flavors</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      You can't go wrong with our flavor options. From rich chocolate to sweet cinnamon, each flavor is sure to impress! Can't find what you want? We often create custom flavors — ask when placing
      your order. We also offer gluten, dairy, egg, and sugar free options.*
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-brand-light-cream">
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Classic Flavors</h4>
      <ul class="list-with-svgs mt-2 text-sm space-y-1">
        <li class="white-cake duration-200 hover:scale-103">White</li>
        <li class="yellow-cake duration-200 hover:scale-103">Yellow</li>
        <li class="chocolate-cake duration-200 hover:scale-103">Chocolate</li>
        <li class="red-velvet-cake duration-200 hover:scale-103">Red Velvet</li>
        <li class="strawberry-cake duration-200 hover:scale-103">Strawberry</li>
        <li class="marble-cake duration-200 hover:scale-103">Marble (swirl of two flavors)</li>
      </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-brand-light-cream">
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Bold Flavors</h4>
      <ul class="list-with-svgs mt-2 text-sm space-y-1">
        <li class="lime-cake duration-200 hover:scale-103">Lime</li>
        <li class="lemon-cake duration-200 hover:scale-103">Lemon</li>
        <li class="raspberry-cake duration-200 hover:scale-103">Raspberry</li>
        <li class="mocha-flavor duration-200 hover:scale-103">Mocha</li>
        <li class="coffee-flavor duration-200 hover:scale-103">Coffee</li>
        <li class="cinnamon-flavor duration-200 hover:scale-103">Cinnamon</li>
      </ul>
      </div>  
    </div>
  </section>

  </section>

  <!-- Frosting Types -->
  <section class="rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm bg-[url('/swiss-meringue-buttercream.avif')] bg-cover bg-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 !text-brand-dark-brown">Frosting</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-brand-dark-brown font-semibold rounded-md">It is the icing on top... literally! We provide custom color and flavor options. Choose from classic or specialty frostings. We tint and flavor frostings to match your design — final color may differ
      slightly.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-brand-light-cream">
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Classic Frostings</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">American Buttercream</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Italian Buttercream</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Sugar Free Buttercream (made with monk fruit)</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Cream Cheese</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-brand-light-cream">
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Specialty Frostings*</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Ganache (White, Milk, or Dark)</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Whipped Cream</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Fondant</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Frosting Flavor Additions -->
  <section class="rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm bg-[url('/how-to-melt-chocolate.avif')] bg-cover bg-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 !text-brand-light-cream">Frosting Flavor Additions</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-light-cream rounded-md">Add any of these flavors to your frosting for an additional kick of flavor. These are just a few of our options. Contacts us if you have something else in
      mind. The possibilities are endless!</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-brand-light-cream">
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Decadent</h4>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Chocolate</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Salted Caramel</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Maple</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Bourbon</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-brand-light-cream">
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Fruit & Citrus</h4>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Strawberry</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Raspberry</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Blackberry</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Lemon</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Lime</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Orange</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-brand-light-cream">
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Spices & Essences</h4>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Cinnamon</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Ginger</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Lavender</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Rosewater</li>
          <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Peppermint</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Fillings -->
  <section class="rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm bg-[url('/easy-homemade-blueberry-pie-filling.avif')] bg-cover bg-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 !text-white">Fillings*</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-white font-semibold rounded-md">Surprise your guests with our delightful cake fillings. Each filling perfectly balances out your cake's flavor and texture. We also offer fresh fruit and other flavors on request. Note: Fresh fruit is not
      recommended for outdoor parties during the summer months.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
       <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-brand-light-cream">
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Sweet and Fruity</h4>
      <ul class="mt-2 text-sm space-y-1">
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Strawberry</li>
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Raspberry</li>
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Blackberry</li> 
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Peach</li>
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Cherry</li>
      </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-brand-light-cream">
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Rich and Creamy</h4>
      <ul class="mt-2 text-sm space-y-1">
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Chocolate Ganache</li>
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">White Chocolate Ganache</li>
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Caramel</li>
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Chocolate Mousse</li>
        <li class="duration-200 hover:scale-103">Vanilla Mousse</li>
      </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">*Additional fees may apply</p>
  <!-- Signature Gourmet Cakes (Sara's specialties) -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-4">Signature Gourmet Cakes — Sara's Specialties</h2>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">These are our specialty designs and flavor combinations — perfect for
      celebrations where you want something unique and memorable.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Brown sugar cake filled with egg-less chocolate chip cookie dough.
            Frosted with salted vanilla buttercream or chocolate ganache.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">May I Have S'more</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Graham cracker cake filled with chocolate ganache. Frosted with toasted
            marshmallow frosting and topped with ganache drip.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Triple Berry Lemon</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Light and fluffy lemon cake with whole blueberries. Filled with a layer
            of
            strawberry, and a layer of raspberry Italian buttercream. Frosted in lemon
            Italian buttercream.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Ube Dream</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">This boba tea inspired cake is made with real ube! It is an ube sponge
            filled with vanilla mousse and frosted in an ube and
            mascarpone buttercream. It's naturally purple!</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 5 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Chocolate Chai</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Our delicious chocolate cake mixed with real black tea, cardamom,
            cinnamon, ginger, and black pepper. Filled and frosted in Chai tea Italian
            buttercream. Topped with chocolate ganache drip.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 6 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Chocolate Bourbon</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Contains alcohol, for adults only Super moist chocolate cake infused
            with real bourbon whiskey. Filled with
            chocolate ganache. Topped with chocolate bourbon buttercream.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4 text-center">Other Specialties</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 7 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Blackberry Peach</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Vanilla cake filled with a house made peach preserve. Frosted with
            blackberry buttercream and topped with a fresh blackberry (subject to seasonal availability).</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 8 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Honey Ginger</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Delicious honey cake infused with ginger. Filled with a Greek yogurt
            honey mousse and frosted in a whipped white chocolate ganache. Bump it up with an extra splash of orange
            zest for an addition burst of flavor (optional).</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 9 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Maple Bacon</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Vanilla cake with real bacon crumbles inside. Filled and frosted with
            maple Italian buttercream and topped with real crispy bacon strips.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 10 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Cherry Lime</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Lime flavored cake with cherry filling. Topped with cherry lime
            buttercream and a maraschino cherries.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 11 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Margarita</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Contains alcohol, for adults only. Lime flavored cake infused with real
            tequila. Frosted with tequila lime buttercream and sprinkled with salt.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 12 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Black Forest</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Contains alcohol, for adults only. Thin layers of chocolate cake infused
            with cherry Kirsch. Alternately layered with cherry filling and whipped cream. Frosted in whipped cream and
            topped with maraschino cherries and chocolate shavings.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 13 -->
      <article class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Lucky Clover</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Contains alcohol, for adults only. Green Velvet cake layered with rich
            mint chocolate ganache filling. Frosted with Bailey's Irish Cream frosting.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-brand-dark-brown">
      <p>
        Want a custom version of a signature cake? Contact us to discuss flavors,
        dietary needs, and custom decor.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact"
        class="inline-block mt-3 bg-brand-teal text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-brand-grey-green">Request a
        quote</a>
    </div>

  </section>
</main>

</Page>